</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='file' href='#file'></a> file</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>A local path to a document. Either this or the <code>url</code> configuration option is required.</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='caption' href='#caption'></a> caption</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>The title of the document.</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='username' href='#username'></a> username</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Username for a URL which require HTTP authentication.</p>
